            [1] = {
                ["title1"] = "问题反馈方式",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/公告头图11-功能说明-问题反馈方式 (2).png\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"F6KAdkpSvofJaBxtCwWcukTlnKd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnRY6Mk5dWfM5Z8uVAlT0n7g\">亲爱的狩月人：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnEjcf3twByezeyTeEyRMzRd\">「先遣服测试服」现已开启，狩月人在测试过程中遇到任何问题或建议想法，都可以通过以下方式进行反馈。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcndzggQnFavAKwp4eUE5Rynh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn8PNksHaTPmDAJaGoUxUpHb\"><strong>★建议与BUG反馈方式★</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnyeDVIMDU4Boker6b4Xseaf\">✦ 问卷填写</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcngEjNcgxUpQV0TncRox91zf\">1、进入反馈问卷地址【<a href=\"https://herogames.feishu.cn/share/base/form/shrcnKikJeUpMP2CwxELNja8tzb\" data-lark-is-custom=\"true\">游戏建议</a>】【<a href=\"https://herogames.feishu.cn/share/base/form/shrcnIWnMXrRVUItsS1uuTonvkd\" data-lark-is-custom=\"true\">BUG反馈</a>】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnwn1mMHpmya1qUFhQJCWBXc\">2、填写反馈内容（如截图无法直接看出问题，希望可以附上复现的录屏）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcntbr0fSF3glILdqW02XzrPg\">3、填写设备信息与联系方式</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn4XOIN3eFHpdaYTPitdY6od\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnzgd36lsmyQBzcv9TcUeBQg\">欢迎各位狩月人踊跃提供意见和建议，帮助我们持续优化游戏体验，共同建设一个更好的《二重螺旋》。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnA45OklaP22YDGsSlee0qWg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnI5sIMx0IvzTuJV5KOPsIX1\">《二重螺旋》运营团队</div>\n</div>",
