            [1] = {
                ["title1"] = "【皎皎的支援】测试特别活动",
                ["body"] = "<div data-page-id=\"FthcdjiX2oLu9FxcjrKcWZ5knGg\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HG8EdAdBqoTEDuxMO1zchGBinRL\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/皎皎的特别支援.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HG8EdAdBqoTEDuxMO1zchGBinRL\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HG8EdAdBqoTEDuxMO1zchGBinRL\">亲爱的狩月人：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CJ9ddcHGio7HyTxFEFmczcokntc\">测试期间，为了给各位狩月人带来更愉快的游戏体验，我们将发放以下邮件内容，感谢对二重螺旋的关注与支持。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PZqBdxOenoFSfPxCi6Gcyaamnbf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YwRNdbVUBoKFjEx8wWyc6fShn4f\">◆ 测试感谢礼</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LJWCd31ruoe8YLxtusSc1ly6naf\">为感谢狩月人参与本次测试，解锁邮件系统后，可通过邮件直接领取「月石晶胚」*100000、「虹色棱镜」*1000。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Wpe5dz7ugozbR8x6FXbcVydFnAc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AslzdrbPhoByQ9xaYxGcspHyn6c\">随着测试进度，后续会逐渐新增额外的测试资源，敬请期待。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Do2Fdxla1o46jBxXEpWc0h3cnLh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JDLVd7kXxoT7CJxZfxqcOoc0nCd\">《二重螺旋》运营团队</div>\n</div>",
                ["language"] = "CN",
                ["title"] = "【皎皎的支援】测试特别活动",
            },
        },
